Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,人数为3人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话是来不及的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁掩护了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,干比古  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,达也
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================STAFF====================
